lore: Vanguard organisms for the Tyranid hive fleets, Purestrain Genestealers are one of the most lethal life forms in the galaxy. They combine the cunning of an apex predator with inhuman speed and agility, closing with their prey in the blink of an eye before tearing their victims to bloody tatters.

otherAbilities.Swift and Deadly:: This unit is eligible to declare a charge in a turn in which it Advanced .
